ied)", "work": "Selections (unspecified)", "composer": null, "performers": [{"id": "2665", "name": "Slide Hampton", "qid": "Q1369035", "roles": ["trombone"]}, {"id": "2687", "name": "Gary Smulyan", "qid": "Q1494952", "roles": ["baritone_saxophone"]}, {"id": "2688", "name": "Lew Soloff", "qid": "Q590792", "roles": ["trumpet"]}, {"id": "14861", "name": "Bruce Hornsby", "qid": "Q918502", "roles": ["piano"]}, {"id": "17131", "name": "Dennis Irwin", "qid": "Q984085", "roles": ["double_bass"]}, {"id": "17365", "name": "Jerry Dodgion", "qid": "Q1687811", "roles": ["alto_saxophone"]}, {"id": "19749", "name": "Frank Wess", "qid": "Q182792", "roles": ["saxophone"]}, {"id": "22175", "name": "Alex Foster", "qid": "Q4717008", "roles": ["tenor_saxophone"]}, {"id": "24936", "name": "Jeff Lorber", "qid": "Q1686336", "roles": ["keyboard"]}, {"id": "32099", "name": "Art Porter", "qid": null, "roles": ["alto_saxophone"]}, {"id": "37077", "name": "Byron Stripling", "qid": "Q19668264", "roles": ["trumpet"]}, {"id": "41583", "name": "Willie Williams", "qid": null, "roles": ["tenor_saxophone"]}, {"id": "43561", "name": "Earl Gardner", "qid": null, "roles": ["trumpet"]}, {"id": "45504", "name": "Dennis Wilson", "qid": null, "roles": ["trombone"]}, {"id": "59968", "name": "Douglas Purviance", "qid": "Q5301901", "roles": ["bass_trombone"]}, {"id": "59983", "name": "Randy Brecker", "qid": "Q48996", "roles": ["trumpet"]}]}], "quotes": [{"speaker": "JJ Johnson", "qid": "Q504915", "text": "Yes. In the next few weeks – as a matter of fact, the exact date is April 6, 1994 – there will be a celebration of 50 years of Jazz at the Philharmonic at Carnegie Hall – a black tie, high profile, prestigious event. They are even calling it the musical event of the year at Carnegie Hall in 1994. We’ll see about that. But a lot of people are excited about it. I will be involved. Illinois Jacquet, who was certainly a part of Jazz at the Philharmonic, will be there. A lot of people are on it that were not a part of Jazz at the Philharmonic, to make it a very high profile, prestigious event. I’m told that Shirley Horne is going to be . . . Carolyn, who are some of the other people who are going to be on the Carnegie Hall thing April the 6th? Shirley Horne and who else? CAROLYN JOHNSON: Abbey Lincoln.", "caption": "JJ Johnson recalls performing at the 1994 Jazz at the Philharmonic 50th anniversary celebration", "conf": "high", "first_person": true, "doc_title": "JJ Johnson — Smithsonian Jazz Oral History", "collection": "si", "url": "https://amhistory.si.edu/jazz/Johnson-JJ/Johnson_JJ_Transcript.pdf"}, {"speaker": "JJ Johnson", "qid": "Q504915", "text": "Abbey Lincoln. A lot of people. A lot of people. I have the article here. I'll show it to you. It's interesting. It can explain in much more detail about what April the 6th at Carnegie Hall is all about than I can ever do. We saved it just for that purpose, 'cause I’ve tried a couple of times to explain to people and they say, \"I don’t know what you're talking about.\" [Then I say,] \"Here, read this.\" [And then they say,] \"Oh! Now we know what you mean.\"", "caption": "JJ Johnson recalls the April 6, 1994 Verve Records concert", "conf": "high", "first_person": true, "doc_title": "JJ Johnson — Smithsonian Jazz Oral History", "collection": "si", "url": "https://amhistory.si.edu/jazz/Johnson-JJ/Johnson_JJ_Transcript.pdf"}], "featured_people": [{"qid": "Q231071", "id": "24940", "name": "Abbey Lincoln"}, {"qid": "Q1341043", "id": "55376", "name": "Al Foster"}, {"qid": "Q4717008", "id": "22175", "name": "Alex Foster"}, {"qid": "Q200131", "id": "60544", "name": "Antônio Carlos Jobim"}, {"qid": "Q465943", "id": "50099", "name": "Betty Carter"}, {"qid": "Q918502", "id": "14861", "name": "Bruce Hornsby"}, {"qid": "Q19668264", "id": "37077", "name": "Byron Stripling"}, {"qid": "Q319283", "id": "8655", "name": "Charlie Haden"}, {"qid": "Q732319", "id": "26105", "name": "Christian McBride"}, {"qid": "Q233529", "id": "39920", "name": 